---
export const prerender = true;
import BlogLayout from '../../layouts/BlogLayout.astro';
import '../../styles/global.css';
---

<BlogLayout
  title="High-Scoring Scrabble Words — Maximum Points Guide"
  description="The most valuable words in Scrabble ranked by points. Best Q, Z, X, J words, power words by length, and the legendary OXYPHENBUTAZONE. Free guides, no signup."
  keywords="high scoring scrabble words, best scrabble words, highest point words, q words scrabble, z words scrabble, x words scrabble, power words scrabble"
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What is the highest scoring word possible in Scrabble?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "OXYPHENBUTAZONE is theoretically the highest-scoring single word in Scrabble, worth 1,778 points when played across three triple word squares. In practice, the highest verified single-turn score is 365 points for QUIXOTRY played across two triple word squares." }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Which letters score the most points in Scrabble?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Q and Z are worth 10 points each, X and J are worth 8 points each, and K is worth 5 points. Words using these tiles score significantly higher, especially when placed on premium squares that double or triple the letter value." }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What are the best short high-scoring words in Scrabble?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "QI (11 pts), ZA (11 pts), ZO (11 pts), AX (9 pts), XI (9 pts), XU (9 pts), JO (9 pts), and EX (9 pts) are the highest face-value two-letter words. For three letters, ZAX (19 pts), ZEK (16 pts), and QAT (12 pts) lead the pack." }
      }
    ]
  })} />

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <nav class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-6 flex items-center gap-1">
      <a href="/blog" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">← Blog</a>
      <span class="mx-1">›</span>
      <span class="text-gray-300">High-Scoring Words</span>
    </nav>

    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">High-Scoring Scrabble Words</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-8">
      Points win games. These 11 guides focus on the most valuable words in Scrabble — organised by letter, 
      by word length, and by scoring potential. Learn which words to reach for when you need maximum impact, 
      and how to deploy premium tiles (Q, Z, X, J) for devastating scores.
    </p>

    <div class="grid gap-4">
      <a href="/blog/highest-scoring-scrabble-words" class="block p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Highest Scoring Scrabble Words</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">The all-time highest-value words ranked by face value and premium square potential.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/blog/high-scoring-short-words" class="block p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">High-Scoring Short Words</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">2-4 letter words that punch above their weight — maximum points from minimum tiles.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/blog/best-q-words-scrabble" class="block p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Best Q Words in Scrabble</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">All valid Q words including Q-without-U plays — never get stuck with the 10-point tile again.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/blog/best-z-words-scrabble" class="block p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Best Z Words in Scrabble</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">Deploy the Z tile for maximum impact — short plays, bingo setups, and triple-word lane plays.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/blog/best-x-words-scrabble" class="block p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Best X Words in Scrabble</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">The 8-point X tile is versatile — AX, EX, XI, OX plus longer words for big scores.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/blog/best-j-words-scrabble" class="block p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Best J Words in Scrabble</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">JO, JAB, JIN, JEU — the best plays for the 8-point J tile at every word length.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/blog/five-letter-power-words" class="block p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Five-Letter Power Words</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">High-value 5-letter words that combine premium tiles with common letters for reliable big scores.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/blog/highest-scoring-five-letter-words" class="block p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Highest Scoring Five-Letter Words</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">The 5-letter words with the highest base tile values — ranked and analysed for playability.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/blog/highest-scoring-six-letter-words" class="block p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Highest Scoring Six-Letter Words</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">6-letter powerhouses — one tile short of a bingo but still capable of 40+ point plays.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/blog/highest-scoring-seven-letter-words" class="block p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Highest Scoring Seven-Letter Words</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">The 7-letter words with the highest base values — bingo bonus plus premium tile points.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/blog/oxyphenbutazone-highest-scoring-word" class="block p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">OXYPHENBUTAZONE — The Legendary Highest Score</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">The theoretical 1,778-point word — how it works, why it's almost impossible, and real alternatives.</p>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 border-t border-gray-800 pt-8">
      <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">More Categories</h3>
      <div class="grid gap-3">
        <a href="/blog/bingos" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
          <span class="text-blue-400 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Bingos — Master the 50-point bonus plays</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/blog/strategy" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
          <span class="text-blue-400 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Strategy — Advanced tactics and rack management</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/blog/two-letter-words" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
          <span class="text-blue-400 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Two-Letter Words — High-scoring short plays with Q, X, Z</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/blog/three-letter-words" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group">
          <span class="text-blue-400 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Three-Letter Words — ZAX, ZEK, QAT and more power plays</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 p-5 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900/20 to-indigo-900/20 border border-blue-800 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 flex-wrap">
        <p class="text-sm text-blue-300 font-medium">
          🔤 Find the highest-scoring words for your tiles — free, instant, no signup
        </p>
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white text-sm font-semibold transition-colors shadow-sm">
          Open Word Finder →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BlogLayout>
